            "name": "伊爾奧恩 夫阿斯爾 夫爾伊奧斯",
            "typeId": "c547-1836-d8a-ff4f",
            "typeName": "Unit",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "2c1e-850c-46cc-a167"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "While 此模型 is leading a unit, models in 該單位 have the 不覺疼痛 5+ ability",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "爾伊特艾斯 of 特艾姆普爾伊恩格",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "219d-340d-6681-ab1"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "While 此模型 is 3 吋內 of one or more friendly 星際戰士 載具 units, it has the Lone Operative ability.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "伊爾奧恩 夫阿斯爾",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "2095-1be1-e5cc-1cee"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "In your 指揮階段, 選擇一個 friendly 星際戰士 載具 model 3 吋內 of this model. That model regains up to 3 lost wounds and, until the start of your next 指揮階段, 每當 that 載具 model 進行一次攻擊, add 1 to the 命中擲骰. You cannot select a unit for this ability that has already been selected for the Blessing of the Omnissiah ability this phase, and vice versa.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "大師 of 斯艾 夫奧爾格艾",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "c393-649d-7810-bcae"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "This model 可加入以下單位:\n\n■ Aggressor Squad\n■ Eradicator Squad\n■ 重型 Intercessor Squad",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "領袖",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "b3b3-c43c-41b1-a086"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "If you include 此模型 in your army, until the end of the battle, non-角色 models in 重型\nIntercessor Squad units 你軍隊中的 have an 目標控制 characteristic of 3 while they are\nnot 戰鬥震懾ed.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "伊恩斯普伊爾伊恩格 克奧姆姆阿恩德爾",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "1d65-986b-9266-a544"
          }
