          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "每當 a model in 此模型’s unit 進行一次攻擊 that targets a 怪獸 or 載具 unit, that\nattack has the [LETHAL HITS] ability. 每當 a model in this model’s unit 進行一次攻擊 that targets any other unit, that attack has the [SUSTAINED HITS 1] ability.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "克奧爾德 阿恩德 克阿爾克烏爾阿特伊恩格",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "10ac-79f8-b15d-f71e"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "■ 在 Declare Battle Formations step, you can 選擇一個 星際戰士 步兵 unit from your army. Until the end of the battle, 該單位 gains the 斥候 6\" ability.\n\n\n■ After both players have deployed their armies, you can 選擇一個 星際戰士 unit 你軍隊中的 and redeploy it. When doing so, you can set 該單位 up in Strategic Reserves if you wish, regardless of how many units are already in Strategic Reserves.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "克爾艾布爾艾克斯 爾奧格伊克 艾恩格伊恩艾",
